---
import ToolPage from '../layouts/ToolPage.astro';
---
<ToolPage
  title="Talk Buddy"
  titleHtml='Talk <span class="brand-mark">Buddy</span>'
  tagline="Practice real-world conversations with an AI partner in a safe, private space where it's OK to stumble."
  description="Practice real-world conversations with an AI partner in a safe, private space where it's OK to stumble."
  brand="talk-buddy"
  repo="michael-borck/talk-buddy"
>

<section class="app-section">
  <h2>What it does</h2>
  <div class="app-features">
    <div class="app-feature">
      <h3>Hold-to-speak</h3>
      <p>Press the mic (or spacebar) to talk. Real-time AI responses with natural speech synthesis.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="app-feature">
      <h3>Scenario library</h3>
      <p>Job interviews, presentations, HR meetings, language drills — or write your own scenarios.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="app-feature">
      <h3>Practice packs</h3>
      <p>Bundle related scenarios into focused practice sessions you can return to anytime.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="app-feature">
      <h3>Transcripts &amp; analysis</h3>
      <p>Every session is saved with a transcript and optional AI feedback you can review later.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="app-feature">
      <h3>Bring your own AI</h3>
      <p>Works with Claude, GPT, Gemini, Groq, or fully offline with Ollama + Piper + Whisper.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="app-feature">
      <h3>Privacy-first</h3>
      <p>All conversations stay on your machine. No telemetry, no accounts, no data leaves the device.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="app-section">
  <h2>How it works</h2>
  <div class="app-steps">
    <div class="app-step">
      <h3>Pick a scenario</h3>
      <p>Choose from the built-in library or write your own — set the role, context, and goals.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="app-step">
      <h3>Hold to speak</h3>
      <p>Press the mic or spacebar and start the conversation. Talk Buddy listens and responds.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="app-step">
      <h3>Get a real reply</h3>
      <p>The AI replies in real time with natural speech, staying in character throughout.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="app-step">
      <h3>Review &amp; improve</h3>
      <p>Read the transcript, request analysis, and try the same scenario again with what you learned.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

</ToolPage>
